特斯拉車輛。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;AMD則大升4.2%，收報144.16美元，受惠英偉達或將重新打開中國市場。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;美匯升報97.51&lt;/span&gt;；美長債息跌報4.346厘。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;中概股指數升0.9%，收報7468點，&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;恒指下個高位24372，10天線24050，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;支持位50天線～23630&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;A股開市軟，昨日高位3526&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;支持位3491&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;北水吸資29億，連續5個交易日吸資&lt;/span&gt;：買建行及阿里，美團；淨流出方面，&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;騰訊及小米&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;港匯觸7.85弱方保證、金管局接132.82億港元總結餘退守千億-&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;拆息會否繼續升？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31979055&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1821855224687075181c8887_91194745"/><published>2025-07-11T09:34:09+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>1765a4846235a15f5421f123246aaf4a</id><title>螞蟻澄清未接入Circle！Coinbase與Perplexity AI合作！Robinhood遭調查</title><updated>2025-07-11T09:44:48+08:00</updated><author><name>modelsx3y</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-11T09:44:48+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573186104"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573186104"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S0-KCGiJl24?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://youtu.be/S0-KCGiJl24" target="_bl