 none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573186367" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250711/20250711_4d44c0955fe71807ba2eG8hyKbMv1AbA.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/a48c48/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250711/20250711_4d44c0955fe71807ba2eG8hyKbMv1AbA.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16358768_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16358768&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FB_IMG_1752199453791.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (168.4 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-7-11 10:04&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31979075&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1821855224687075181c8887_91194745"/><published>2025-07-11T10:04:52+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>ac7535eb70bbf6d08343e2f8a7e4953e</id><title>好很感動，終於升我有貨果隻【國聯民生】</title><updated>2025-07-11T10:13:38+08:00</updated><author><name>一個夢</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-11T10:13:38+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573186500"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573186500"&gt;大落後，但幾個月前已發盈喜&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;利申：本人有貨&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31979088&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1821855224687075181c8887_91194745"/><published>2025-07-11T10:13:38+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c518468ea1257ec9f4e3ac5cfdfdc624</id><title>驚！節食之後開始脫髮</title><updated>2025-07-03T16:26:00+08:00</updated><author><name>劈手指</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-03T16:26:00+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573089310"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573089310"&gt;開始每日食兩餐減肥，其中一餐用代餐嚟代替，點知發現開始脫髮，越甩越多，係咪正常？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31972730&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=57&amp;utm_campaign=1077&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-07-03T16:26:00+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>17fa47c1f366e8fe0d0882253c398141</id><title>驗空腹血糖前的準備</title><updated>2025-06-30T23:38:11+08:00</updated><author><name>dooropener</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-30T23:38:11+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573055510"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573055510"&gt;政府門診驗空腹血糖前4天，自己篤手指驗一下，發覺是 6.2 mmol/L，已經踏進糖尿病前期，大吃一驚。本身沒有糖尿病，一般是 5.0-5.6，歸究是吃了很多荔枝(荔枝大灶)和粥粉麵飯&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;於是馬上戒糖和粥粉麵飯，每天運動半小時，2天後篤手指回落到 5.8，繼續戒糖+運動。去診所前一晚唔食晚飯，即是24小時空腹，估計診所空腹血糖應該正常在 5.4左右，結果出來了，是 4.0 mmol/L，沒有估到噤低。戒糖+運動+1晚斷食真喺可以消耗身體糖份，咁做算唔算呃診所 &lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;🤭&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;注意: 每個人身體不一樣，胰島素分泌量和抗阻不同，代謝有快有慢，我 work 唔代表你 work&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31970456&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=57&amp;utm_campaign=1077&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-06-30T23:38:11+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>307c25d3bc95781f48b804ee288ba62f</id><title>一到weekend 就打噴嚏和流鼻水</title><updated>2025-07-06T21:58:14+08:00</updated><author><name>馬洛耶夫</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-06T21:58:14+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573129608"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573129608"&gt;再近呢一個月, 每到weekend 就狂打噴嚏, 之後就流鼻水,&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;我要好似睇感冒時醫生開的抗敏感藥的食法先可以收到鼻水&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;如早晚一粒fexofenadine + 訓覺前食兩粒Chlorpheniramine Maleate, 但 Chlorpheniramine Maleate 的副作用好大, 加上呢個食法係訓覺前食兩粒Chlorpheniramine Maleate, 所以食完好眼訓, 頭好暈, 但收鼻水好有效&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;另一個方法係早晚一粒Cetirizine+Loratadine, 呢個食法都會有少少眼訓,&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;當收左鼻水之後, 就會出現頭痛, 周身酸痛, 就變成感冒, 又或者無事, 但一到星期五六日又會狂打噴嚏&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;我上年10 月左打流感針, 依家每日飲一杯1000mg 維他命C, 但情況一樣&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;我公司有個0靚仔成日流鼻水+無帶口罩, 但我返工日日都有口罩, 唔通係比佢傳染, 好返之後又比佢傳染?&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;請問有咩方法可以增強低抗力?&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31975472&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=57&amp;utm_campaign=1077&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-07-06T21:58:14+08:00</published></entry></feed>